    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six. This high-revving power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, ensuring structural integrity and timing precision. The chassis is supported by refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers for optimized damping cycles and turn-in response. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals\u2014including consistent compression across all cylinders\u2014confirm this is a high-performance machine ready for the apex. A true enthusiast's specimen optimized for both longitudinal and lateral performance.",
